1.0.name: wordpress/google-calendar-plugin
1.0.description: This plugin show the google calendar in your weblog wordpress admin pannel. You can choose the priveleges must an user needle for use Google Calendar Plugin and you can store a lot of calendar and see what you want in main pannel. An administrator and olny he can share some calendar and all other users see that calendar in admin page.
